{"tid":1454311,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"委內瑞拉16歲示威者眼部中16發橡膠子彈致盲   警官終被控「謀殺未遂」","createTime":"2019-08-12T06:57:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T00:15:25.000Z","uid":79563,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"93940309ff47b54e9cca5fa6ca3fd96a978c8b60","tid":1454311,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:57:59.000Z","msg":"7月2日委內瑞拉的聖克里斯托瓦爾市（San Cristobal）有民眾上街示威，抗議當地的家用煤氣短缺，但最終演變成警民衝突。警方在無預警的情況下對市民進行暴力鎮壓，發射多枚橡膠子彈，其中一名16歲的男青年示威者Rufo Chacon，全身慘中52發，當中16發子彈擊中眼部致盲。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/methode_times_prod_web_bin_fe8a70ae-9da1-11e9-ba8e-fd50a45d027e_9329754425d31730e1e5af.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2Fmethode_times_prod_web_bin_fe8a70ae-9da1-11e9-ba8e-fd50a45d027e_9329754425d31730e1e5af.jpg&h=09f62c47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nRufo Chacon馬上緊急送院，雖然醫生能把眼部的子彈碎片取出來，但也有部分留在腦內及臉部，還有感染的風險。而他的14歲弟弟Adrian頭部也被警察用警棍擊中，他們二人當日是跟著媽媽一同上街示威。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/qv1w1kuanfab_3dusv-4ijoq5bivsbgfck_gxgppxsy_378541985d31741eabbd9.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2Fqv1w1kuanfab_3dusv-4ijoq5bivsbgfck_gxgppxsy_378541985d31741eabbd9.jpeg&h=85e2d821&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n事後警方發出了一份調查報告，指出當日有警員沒有在預警的情況下使用武力，除了Rufo Chacon及弟弟Adrian外，也有另一名未成年者在示威中受到傷害。聯合國人權事務高級專員Michelle Bachelet隨後發出了聲明，指責委內瑞拉政府的行為「違反人權」。最終政府宣布對2名涉事警員作出起訴，分別控告「殺人未遂」、「不當使用武器」、「殘忍行為」等罪行。<br />\n<br />\n但是委內瑞拉總統馬杜羅（Nicolas Maduro）卻反指調查報告並不公正，存有偏見。Rufo Chacon示威後表示：「政治家全部都是騙子，這裡的法律是用來攻擊人民，並不是保護他們。」"},{"pid":"01cf39fb5956e0903bc070d9dae026ccfe29eb3c","tid":1454311,"uid":71237,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T07:02:44.000Z","msg":"香港衰撚過委內瑞拉，起碼佢地仲會調查警方濫用武力。"},{"pid":"bdcade9550f4dd527d05875245cf9e96c2d43357","tid":1454311,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T07:03:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ttLEooS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FttLEooS.png&h=4b443cfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vxZmxjw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvxZmxjw.png&h=1d33d451&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g1fEi4i.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg1fEi4i.png&h=ea27d434&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ad8d7c91846827f01a6cfeede427464bb0ee59d7","tid":1454311,"uid":261705,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T07:03:27.000Z","msg":"收起做案例"},{"pid":"5a79ab7c18a7e4298370053b458802f72c765f15","tid":1454311,"uid":13420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T07:03:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17f11eb7869042f5489eff2d2553ffb9f47961a3","tid":1454311,"uid":14816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T07:04:37.000Z","msg":"16發<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15942e22729d4ca6663a96bc2fded52d68f279c9","tid":1454311,"uid":93277,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T07:04:57.000Z","msg":"講法例香港真係全世界最廢地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c69d92119b00c9632db6e5f9e05fffaea226522","tid":1454311,"uid":81531,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T07:07:54.000Z","msg":"屌 真係估唔到香港而家仲衰過南美國家<br />\n人地獨裁都仲分到法治出黎<br />\n香港法治就變人治<br />\n共產黨真係人類文明毒瘤"},{"pid":"4f3e4139f567df70a02d5b938f66712d1bb950b6","tid":1454311,"uid":201732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"